    com.example.surajbokankar.ssomanager.network.RestApiService.callAuthorizationApi(HashMap<String, String>)
    use RestApiService.callAuthorizationRenewApi(String, RequestBody) instead User login using Oauth2 protocol. Return token, otp, callback_url and users permissions and other info for already logged in user.
